hpnicfMultilinkPPPV2.name: hpnicfMultilinkPPPV2

revisions.description: HPN-ICF-MP-V2-MIB module for managing MP(Multilink PPP).

hpnicfMultilinkPPPV2.description: The HPN-ICF-MP-V2-MIB provides read access to MP(Multilink PPP) link status information. The information available through this MIB includes: the father channel, the bundled son channel, the slot on which son channels are bundled, the number of son channels, the bundle name, the statistics for lost fragments, reordered packets, unassigned packets, interleaved packets, and the received/sent sequence number, etc.

hpnicfMpMultilinkV2Table.name: hpnicfMpMultilinkV2Table
hpnicfMpMultilinkV2Table.description: This table describes the information of MP link. The index of this table is the interface index of MP group or VA (Virtual Access) interface.

hpnicfMpMultilinkV2Entry.name: hpnicfMpMultilinkV2Entry
hpnicfMpMultilinkV2Entry.description: Each entry in this table describes the information of MP link. The available information includes: the father channel, the slot on which son channels are bundled, the number of bundled son channels, the statistics for lost fragments, reordered packets, unassigned packets, interleaved packets, and received/sent sequence number.

hpnicfMpMultilinkDescrV2.name: hpnicfMpMultilinkDescrV2
hpnicfMpMultilinkDescrV2.description: The interface name of the father interface on which son channels are bundled. It is the name of a Virtual Access or an MP group.

hpnicfMpBundleNameV2.name: hpnicfMpBundleNameV2
hpnicfMpBundleNameV2.description: The bundle name of the multilink. When authentication is configured, the bundle name is the authenticated user name; when authentication is not configured, the bundle name is multilink.

hpnicfMpBundledSlotV2.name: hpnicfMpBundledSlotV2
hpnicfMpBundledSlotV2.description: The slot on which son channels are bundled.

hpnicfMpBundledMemberCntV2.name: hpnicfMpBundledMemberCntV2
hpnicfMpBundledMemberCntV2.description: The number of the bundled son channel of the MP link.

hpnicfMpLostFragmentsV2.name: hpnicfMpLostFragmentsV2
hpnicfMpLostFragmentsV2.description: The number of fragments of the MP link discarded because bad fragments were received, or assembling the packet failed, etc.

hpnicfMpReorderedPktsV2.name: hpnicfMpReorderedPktsV2
hpnicfMpReorderedPktsV2.description: The number of reordered incoming packets of the MP link.

hpnicfMpUnassignedPktsV2.name: hpnicfMpUnassignedPktsV2
hpnicfMpUnassignedPktsV2.description: The number of received packets of the MP link waiting for reordering.

hpnicfMpInterleavedPktsV2.name: hpnicfMpInterleavedPktsV2
hpnicfMpInterleavedPktsV2.description: The number of received packets of the MP link interleaved by the packets queued in RTPQ (Real-time Transport Protocol Queue) or LLQ (Low Latency Queue).

hpnicfMpRcvdSequenceV2.name: hpnicfMpRcvdSequenceV2
hpnicfMpRcvdSequenceV2.description: The current sequence number for the MP link to receive.

hpnicfMpSentSequenceV2.name: hpnicfMpSentSequenceV2
hpnicfMpSentSequenceV2.description: The current sequence number for the MP link to send.

hpnicfMpMemberlinkV2Table.name: hpnicfMpMemberlinkV2Table
hpnicfMpMemberlinkV2Table.description: This table describes the information of son channels of the MP link. The index of this table is the interface index of MP group or VA (Virtual Access) interface.

hpnicfMpMemberlinkV2Entry.name: hpnicfMpMemberlinkV2Entry
hpnicfMpMemberlinkV2Entry.description: Each entry in this table describes the information of the bundled son channels of MP link. The available information includes: the interface index of the son channel, the interface name of the son channel.

hpnicfMpMemberlinkSeqNumberV2.name: hpnicfMpMemberlinkSeqNumberV2
hpnicfMpMemberlinkSeqNumberV2.description: The bundled sequence number of the son channels of the MP link. This object is one of the index of the table.

hpnicfMpMemberlinkIfIndexV2.name: hpnicfMpMemberlinkIfIndexV2
hpnicfMpMemberlinkIfIndexV2.description: The interface index of the son channels of the MP link.

hpnicfMpMemberlinkDescrV2.name: hpnicfMpMemberlinkDescrV2
hpnicfMpMemberlinkDescrV2.description: The interface name of the son channels of the MP link.

hpnicfMpMemberlinkMpStatusV2.name: hpnicfMpMemberlinkMpStatusV2
hpnicfMpMemberlinkMpStatusV2.description: The MP status of the son channels of the MP link.
